            <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
            <p class="last-updated">Last updated: July 17, 2025</p>

            <h2>1. General Policy</h2>
            <p>Our primary goal is your satisfaction. We handle refunds on a case-by-case basis to ensure fairness. The conditions below outline general eligibility for refunds.</p>

            <h2>2. Full Refunds</h2>
            <p>You are eligible for a full refund on a lesson package under the following conditions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The refund request is made within 7 days of the initial purchase date.</li>
                <li>No more than one lesson from the package has been completed.</li>
                <li>A scheduled lesson is cancelled by the instructor, and you choose not to reschedule.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Partial Refunds</h2>
            <p>A partial refund for the value of remaining, unused lessons in a package may be granted if you decide to discontinue the lessons. The refunded amount will be calculated on a pro-rata basis, minus any applied package discounts.</p>
            
            <h2>4. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
            <p>Refunds will generally not be provided in the following cases:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>For lessons that have already taken place.</li>
                <li>For lessons missed by the student without providing at least 24 hours' notice (as per our cancellation policy in the Terms of Service).</li>
                <li>For refund requests made more than 30 days after the purchase date.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. How to Request a Refund</h2>
            <p>To request a refund, please email us at <a href="mailto:admin@clearn.top">admin@clearn.top</a> with your purchase details and the reason for your request. We will review your request within 3-5 business days and notify you of the outcome.</p>
            
            <p>Approved refunds will be processed back to the original payment method within 7-10 business days.</p>
            
